Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Every time I see these reports about violence against polio workers I have serious problems understanding the psyches of individuals who would deprive life saving measures such as vaccinations from vulnerable populations. I was under the impression that an accord had been reached with the Taliban that resulted in a cessation of attacks against vaccinators. Either the accord has broken down or there are new players on the scene continuing the barbaric practices. - Mod.MPP]
